This can be our next projects!

Let's build it as soon as posible.

EDI integration is not a radical or new concept. The drive to reduce manual processing and minimize costly errors has been a key objective for business organizations as long as Electronic Data Interchange (EDI) has been in existence. To gain control over the supply chain, exchanging transaction data with key trading partners in an automated, integrated, and seamless manner is simply the beginning. To be at its most effective, integrated EDI must provide management with a clear, validated means of relating investment in the software, procedures, and countless tasks associated with managing EDI, in concise and quantifiable financial benefits. DiTranslator is an EDI translation software that enables users to transform EDI data to and from the different formats used by your organization. For over two decades, DiTranslator, DiCentral's EDI translation tool, has been powering the EDI and data integration of companies around the world. Over 2,000 organizations rely on this software to process daily transactions and move critical data between systems. Additionally, DiTranslator offers our complete library of pre-built Trading Partner Kits that allow one-click access to establish an EDI framework with any retailer or trading organization.
